query('"2021-01" <= ym <= "2021-10"').\
melt(id_vars = 'ym').rename(columns = {'variable':'prov', 'value':'confirmed'})

_df = _df.assign(pop = [df3.query('prov == @_df["prov"][@i]')['pop'].pipe(int) for i in range(len(_df))]).\
eval('prop = confirmed / pop')
